Subject: [Caml-list] [ANN] Argot: 1.0-beta release

Dear list,

This post announces the 1.0-beta release of the Argot project, whose goal is to provide
enhanced HTML generator for ocamldoc, released under the GPL v3.

Home page: http://argot.x9c.fr

Main changes since 1.0-alpha:
  - switch to OCaml 3.12.1
  - support for folding
  - enhanced support for tables (horizontal span, check for well-formedness)
  - @copyright and @license tags for legal information
  - '-argot-version' command-line switch
  - tests for base64 encoding
  - support for ocamlfind has been fixed
  - support for use as native plugin has been fixed


Xavier Clerc


